<body class="font-['helvetica_now_display'] text-black bg-gray-100">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">Welcome to our IMAZINE. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>
            
            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p class="mb-2">We collect the following types of personal information when you use our services:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-2">
                    <li>Name and contact details (email, phone number)</li>
                    <li>Shipping and billing address</li>
                    <li>Payment information (handled securely)</li>
                    <li>Browsing and purchase history</li>
                    <li>Preferences and interests</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use your information to provide a personalized shopping experience and improve our services. This includes:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-2">
                    <li>Processing and fulfilling orders</li>
                    <li>Handling returns and customer support</li>
                    <li>Sending promotional offers, updates, and newsletters</li>
                    <li>Analyzing browsing data to improve our website</li>
                    <li>Protecting against fraud</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement strict security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, and disclosure. We use encryption and secure protocols for handling sensitive data like payment information.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
                <p>Your personal information is only shared with trusted third-party partners, such as payment processors and shipping providers, to complete your purchases. We do not sell or rent your information to third parties.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
                <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your shopping experience and provide relevant product recommendations. You can control cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal information at any time. If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact our support team.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices. Please review this page periodically for any updates.</p>
            </section>

            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@fashionstore.com" class="text-blue-600">support@Mazn.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

